<div class="home-content row">
  <div class="top-text">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h1>Improving your organization's communication is as easy as 1-2-3</h1>
      <div class="buttons">
        <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn home-button-left" %>
       <a href="#more" class="smoothscroll"><button class="home-button-right">Learn more</button></a>
      </div>
</div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div class="top-content">
   
    <h2>Step 1 ==> Create an account</h2>

      <p>Provide an email address and password to create an account for the BOLD Projects Database. You will not receive any email or any other unwanted communication when you create this account.</p>

    <h2>Step 2 ==> Submit a new project proposal</h2>

      <p>If you have a project idea that you think would be perfect for a technical communication course, complete the proposal form. Previous BOLD projects have included website redesigns, comprehensive edits of organizational documents, and marketing research reports.</p>

    <h2>Step 3 ==> Connect with an instructor</h2>
        <p>If your proposal is suitable for one of our courses, someone will approve and match your project to a particular course. Then, you'll be able to connect with an instructor to work out the major details of the project.</p>
    
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="home-bottom">
<div class="row">

  <h2><a name="more"></a>Why be a BOLD partner?</h2>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <%= image_tag 'code.fw.png' %>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Web-based Projects</h3>
        <p>BOLD, or Business Opportunity and Leadership Development, is a partnership program created to provide opportunities for businesses and non-profit organizations to with with university students. In this mutually beneficial program, students have an oppourtunity to work on real-world client projects, and clients are provided with value-added communication projects. BOLD projects have ranged from website design and development projects to comprehensive editing projects.</p>
        <p>Students have worked on a variety web-related projects including full website redesigns for clients. Projects typically use the Wordpress content management system, but we are flexible to meet client needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <%= image_tag 'people.fw.png' %>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Support students while supporting your business</h3>
        <p>Allowing students to work on real-world projects not only exposes them to essential experience, it provides real benefits to your business.</p>
  
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <%= image_tag 'documents.fw.png' %>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Technical communication is essential to your organization.</h3>
        <p>Previous client projects have added value to many organizations. Previous projects have included editing, graphic design, marketing, technical documentation, and more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>